Section: libs
Homepage: http://libmodbus.org/
Vcs-Git: git@github.com:stephane/libmodbus.git
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/stephane/libmodbus.git

Package: libmodbus-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libmodbus, ${misc:Depends}
Description: A Modbus library for Linux, Mac OS X, FreeBSD, QNX and Windows
 libmodbus is a free software library to send/receive data with a device which respects the Modbus protocol. This library can use a serial port or an Ethernet connection.

